/>\n<br />\n醫管局：對於係 QEH 門口摧淚煙放題，導致急症服務要暫停，對於質疑院內受摧淚氣體污染，危害員工及病人健康，無半句說法，只係話唔應該係院內戴黑口罩同舉行集會，以免影響病人心情。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台：記者日日面對槍林彈雨水深火熱，警察打記者阻採訪無日無之。處長同同事講：「在採訪過程中，不應參與與採訪無關的活動，以免影響外界對本台新聞報道公正持平的觀感。」<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就係宜家嘅香港，無一個嘅所謂專業人士能夠謹守自己嘅專業態度，在高位嘅教授、醫生、律師、公務員全部都放棄左自己嘅專業尊嚴，向極權膜拜。<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅禮崩樂壞已經無法挽回。<br />\n<br />\n#手動轉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"推翻香港政府"},{"pid":"53dc93fb9ff5ef0c323b4ddc6616cd36713a14d5","tid":1742612,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f42b4a64a8e7e7661868c54278c34aa77994e0","tid":1742612,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181646477fbdaa50d483cb1a207eb5648b4fa9db","tid":1742612,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"全部局長 爭住同警務處含撚咁"},{"pid":"d6a1333cfbd508d4693c48ee81000e97f89b7dde","tid":1742612,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}